---
title: Cheesy Tex-Mex Chicken & Potato Chips with Sour Cream
description: Add flavour to every part of your meal with some mild spices, cooling cream and a sprinkling of cheese, pan-seared chicken thigh is transformed into a fiesta of flavour, with a crunchy corn salad on the side to add a fresh touch.
